        <header/>
        <body>
            <trans-unit id="mlang_tabs_tab">
                <source>Agentation</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="mlang_labels_tablabel">
                <source>Agentation</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="mlang_labels_tabdescr">
                <source>Manage the agentation MCP config, inspect status, and review which users have the toolbar enabled.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="mod.tabs.label">
                <source>Agentation</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.heading">
                <source>Configure your AI agent for Agentation</source>
            </trans-unit>

            <trans-unit id="module.intro.title">
                <source>Connect your coding agent to Agentation</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.intro.text">
                <source>{count, plural, one {Complete # step below} other {Complete # steps below}} to stream visual UI annotations from this site into your AI coding agent. Copy the MCP config into your IDE, flip the toolbar toggles, annotate, ship.</source>
            </trans-unit>

            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.heading">
                <source>MCP configuration</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.intro">
                <source>Paste the block below into your coding agent's MCP config (Claude Code ~/.claude/mcp.json, Cursor settings, Windsurf, Zed, Continue). Annotations flow directly to your agent — no copy/paste.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.label">
                <source>MCP server JSON</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.hint">
                <source>Pre-filled with the API key + workspace from Extension Configuration.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.copy">
                <source>Copy to clipboard</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.docs">
                <source>MCP docs</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.addToCursor">
                <source>Add to Cursor</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.claudeCliLabel">
                <source>Claude Code — one-line CLI install</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.claudeCliHint">
                <source>Paste into a terminal where the `claude` CLI is installed to register the MCP server.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.noApiKey">
                <source>No API key configured. MCP only works in authenticated mode — set Agentation.apiKey in Extension Configuration.</source>
            </trans-unit>

            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.heading">
                <source>Stored annotations</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.intro">
                <source>Every annotation you make is stored in your browser's localStorage, scoped per BE module + record. You can delete every stored annotation across every scope in one click.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.loading">
                <source>Loading…</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.empty">
                <source>No annotations</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.emptyLong">
                <source>Nothing stored yet. Annotations created via the toolbar appear here.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.onlyLocal">
                <source>No server-side annotations. Local annotations are stored only in this browser.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.errorPrefix">
                <source>Sync endpoint unreachable</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.errorShort">
                <source>Sync endpoint unreachable</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.onServer">
                <source>on server</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.local">
                <source>local</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.singular">
                <source>annotation</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.plural">
                <source>annotations</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.emptyComment">
                <source>(no comment)</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.deleteOne">
                <source>Delete annotation</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.deleteAll">
                <source>Delete all stored annotations</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.annotations.reload">
                <source>Reload annotations</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.heading">
                <source>How to use</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.summary">
                <source>{count, plural, one {# step} other {# steps}} from install to first annotation.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.toggleShow">
                <source>Show step-by-step instructions</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.step1">
                <source>Paste the MCP JSON above into your coding agent's config and restart the agent.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.step2">
                <source>Enable the toolbar: frontend via the TYPO3 Admin Panel, backend via User Settings → Agentation tab.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.step3">
                <source>Click the floating bubble, pick an element, write a note — Agentation captures selectors, file paths and computed styles.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.step4">
                <source>Your agent receives the annotation through MCP and resolves it against the codebase directly.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.readDocs">
                <source>Read the full MCP docs</source>
            </trans-unit>

